# Mac/Linux
cp -r justice-client-portal justice-client-portal-backup

Tip 3: Use VS Code

    Download VS Code: https://code.visualstudio.com/
    Open project folder: File → Open Folder
    View all files in sidebar
    Easy editing and navigation

